Title: Marine One
Plot: While Carrie is near catatonic and confined to bed, Saul investigates the unsettling implications of her timeline; Walker secures a perch for his mission; Brody makes his final preparations for the Vice President's policy summit at the State Department.
GuestStars: Linda Purl, David Marciano, Jamey Sheridan, Amy Hargreaves, Hrach Titizian, Chris Chalk, Navid Negahban
